data.description: Welcome to this Exquisite 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence, a true gem in the realm of real estate!! Nestled in the desirable Providence Golf Club Community. This remarkable property offers an unparalleled combination comfort and magnificence. You will enjoy the meticulous thoughtfully designed spaces, it presents a perfect haven for those seeking the ultimate residential experience. The main level features a seamless flow, with each room exuding an inviting ambiance. Home features ceramic tiles in all main areas, carpet in bedrooms, living/dinning room combo, large kitchen area with spacious island and an additional space for a breakfast nook. All stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, hanging pot rack, 42" inch wood cabinets with crown molding. Family room is adjacent to kitchen allowing for gatherings and family time to be as fun as they can be! Enjoy the covered lanai and fenced backyard with no rear neighbors. Guest bedroom conveniently located on the first level with a full bathroom. All bathrooms countertops are granite. On the second level, home features considerable large master bedroom, bath has a walk in shower with separate tub and dual sinks. His and hers walk in closets. Ample laundry room. Exterior painted June 2023. Water Heater is Hybrid. This 24-hour manned gated community, Resort style gives you access to a golf course, clubhouse with a bar/restaurant, a newly renovated fitness center, resort pools, tennis courts, walking trails, playground, and dog park. Conveniently located to shopping, highways, schools and more!! Call to schedule your private showing today.
